WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes‚Ä¶

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 20]

02:55.170 --> 02:56.770
Thank you for your help, Grand Master.

02:56.790 --> 02:58.060
If it weren't for you, Grand Master,

02:58.170 --> 03:00.380
I, Chen Ye, would have been killed by Jing Lei.

03:02.450 --> 03:04.080
Being humble

03:04.100 --> 03:05.330
doesn't seem

03:05.350 --> 03:06.580
to match you well.

03:06.990 --> 03:08.670
You knew for a fact

03:08.690 --> 03:09.900
that I won't let you die,

03:10.650 --> 03:13.160
That's why you dared to

03:13.180 --> 03:15.060
head to the Cold Spring Palace.

03:16.020 --> 03:17.990
Originally, if we kill a few more humans,

03:18.140 --> 03:19.860
the evil insect could have been transmuted.

03:20.020 --> 03:21.180
Unfortunately,

03:21.630 --> 03:23.460
the old guy in Lanling interrupted me.

03:23.490 --> 03:24.320
Enough.

03:24.640 --> 03:26.079
The Supreme Eternal

03:26.110 --> 03:27.600
came in person to capture you.

03:28.160 --> 03:29.790
You're considered prestigious now.

03:29.930 --> 03:31.820
But don't you think it's strange, Grand Master?

03:31.970 --> 03:34.030
We've been very careful.

03:34.660 --> 03:36.500
How could he know it in advance?

03:36.990 --> 03:37.940
Besides,

03:38.240 --> 03:39.750
how could he recognise

03:39.780 --> 03:41.250
that I'm from the Cold Spring Palace?

03:42.130 --> 03:43.410
Unless...

03:44.960 --> 03:47.000
Chong Zhao is also from Lanling.

03:51.970 --> 03:53.410
It's about time

03:53.620 --> 03:55.030
the both of them return.

04:06.740 --> 04:08.130
Why are you still here?

04:09.760 --> 04:11.320
I didn't hurt the people from the Fox Clan.

04:12.200 --> 04:13.200
Shuo.

04:14.060 --> 04:16.050
I should have told you some things earlier.

04:17.360 --> 04:18.329
I'm sorry.

04:18.930 --> 04:20.779
So are you going to tell me

04:20.940 --> 04:22.890
why you wanted to enter the Cold Spring Palace?

04:22.920 --> 04:24.580
If I say it's for Lanling,

04:25.130 --> 04:25.860
would you believe me?

04:35.050 --> 04:36.350
Young Lord,

04:36.450 --> 04:38.310
Chong Zhao went to find Bai Shuo again.

04:38.340 --> 04:39.980
Stop helping him, Young Lord.

04:40.000 --> 04:42.350
Master will punish you severely when we're back.

04:42.380 --> 04:43.230
Perhaps,

04:43.250 --> 04:44.280
he might even kill you.

04:44.310 --> 04:45.280
Don't worry.

04:45.300 --> 04:46.610
Until the last moment,

04:46.640 --> 04:48.120
I may not necessarily lose.

04:48.170 --> 04:50.280
Young Master, you have an idea?

04:50.310 --> 04:51.310
The incident with Emotion Tree

04:51.360 --> 04:52.420
is sufficient to hault Fan Yue.

04:52.440 --> 04:54.960
We just need to find a chance to kill Bai Shuo.

04:54.990 --> 04:56.060
Just that...

04:56.080 --> 04:58.060
Just that Chong Zhao likes Bai Shuo so much.

04:58.090 --> 04:59.500
He must hate you till death.

04:59.540 --> 05:01.000
This is unfair.

05:01.030 --> 05:02.660
Young Lord, stop liking him.

05:02.680 --> 05:03.820
He is not good at all.

05:03.860 --> 05:05.300
-Xixi hates him.
-You‚Äôre right.

05:05.330 --> 05:06.580
So this time

05:06.850 --> 05:08.850
will be the last time I help him.

05:11.520 --> 05:13.560
My feelings ripple,

05:13.690 --> 05:16.170
but I dare to attempt reversing the river's flow.

05:16.590 --> 05:17.820
I can't control my heart

05:17.870 --> 05:19.660
because it doesn't hurt enough.

05:19.680 --> 05:21.560
It should hurt to my bones;

05:21.590 --> 05:22.830
Hurts so much that I fear;

05:22.850 --> 05:25.170
Hurts so much that whenever I think of the torture,

05:25.200 --> 05:26.850
I no longer dare to waver.

05:27.200 --> 05:28.030
This way,

05:28.480 --> 05:29.710
my feelings for him

05:30.010 --> 05:31.120
will be suppressed.

05:31.710 --> 05:32.390
Young...

05:32.420 --> 05:34.380
Young Master, what do you plan to do?

05:34.400 --> 05:36.100
To kill Bai Shuo,

05:36.330 --> 05:37.790
which is also to bring an end

05:39.550 --> 05:41.300
to my feelings.

05:43.310 --> 05:45.350
You investigated the Cold Spring for Lanling.

05:45.380 --> 05:46.590
That's not odd.

05:46.720 --> 05:49.040
But the Cold Spring Palace

05:49.060 --> 05:50.700
treats other Eternals very harshly.

05:51.350 --> 05:53.280
How did they come to trust you?

05:54.530 --> 05:56.320
It's probably because of Fu Ling.

05:56.560 --> 05:58.120
She wanted me to become a demon.

05:58.450 --> 06:00.770
So she may have said a lot of good words to Zhen Yu.

06:00.880 --> 06:01.860
Become a demon?

06:02.510 --> 06:03.310
You're an Eternal.

06:03.330 --> 06:04.530
How can you become a demon

06:04.550 --> 06:06.180
Through practicing the techniques of the Demon Race?

06:06.320 --> 06:07.520
It's complicated.

06:07.820 --> 06:08.780
Anyway,

06:08.960 --> 06:11.350
Zhen Yu took a fancy to our relationship.

06:11.370 --> 06:13.310
He wants to use me to capture you to the Cold Spring.

06:13.330 --> 06:15.130
All the more reason you shouldn't return then.

06:15.530 --> 06:17.620
They didn't manage to catch me at the Jingyou Mountain this time.

06:17.640 --> 06:19.240
Zhen Yu won't let you go easily.

06:19.660 --> 06:21.260
You should back to Lanling now.

06:21.290 --> 06:22.740
With Sect Leader Jin Yao,

06:22.820 --> 06:23.950
you'll be safe.

06:24.090 --> 06:25.620
I would be. But what about you?

06:25.900 --> 06:27.580
There are so many demons in the Cold Spring Palace.

06:27.610 --> 06:29.490
Zhen Yu is determined to get the Contemplation Stone.

06:29.610 --> 06:31.490
Even if he didn't send me, he would send someone else.

06:31.520 --> 06:32.700
Only when I'm around,

06:32.960 --> 06:34.310
it is safer for you.

06:38.460 --> 06:39.310
Chong Zhao,

06:40.690 --> 06:42.159
You should walk your own path.

06:44.040 --> 06:45.230
What do you mean?

06:45.570 --> 06:46.640
I know

06:47.130 --> 06:48.520
you feel guilty

06:48.540 --> 06:49.880
for what happened to my father at Ning'an City,

06:50.070 --> 06:51.860
that is why you always put me first.

06:52.400 --> 06:53.840
But you don't have to do that.

06:55.130 --> 06:56.370
Aren't you and I

06:56.870 --> 06:58.280
always like this?

06:58.490 --> 06:59.540
Yes.

07:00.030 --> 07:01.710
You have been like this since young

07:02.100 --> 07:04.140
You took the blame when I caused trouble.

07:02.210 --> 07:05.070
‚ôęI remember that moonlit night‚ôę

07:04.170 --> 07:06.340
When my father punished me, you stepped in to defend me.

07:05.910 --> 07:08.450
‚ôęThe flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime‚ôę

07:06.360 --> 07:08.060
I remember these to heart.

07:08.400 --> 07:10.230
But that was in the past.

07:09.270 --> 07:13.030
‚ôęI remember that word of concern‚ôę

07:11.480 --> 07:12.270
You haven't changed.

07:12.290 --> 07:13.630
Neither have I.

07:13.660 --> 07:16.900
‚ôęBut unfortunately, I didn't get to answer‚ôę

07:13.690 --> 07:15.100
What's the difference

07:15.380 --> 07:16.820
from then to now?

07:17.400 --> 07:20.050
‚ôęI remember that drop of tear‚ôę

07:18.620 --> 07:19.790
Now...

07:20.970 --> 07:24.360
‚ôęIt dried in the wind‚ôę

07:23.170 --> 07:24.360
Now I know

07:24.360 --> 07:25.560
that the road ahead is tough,

07:25.040 --> 07:26.690
‚ôęThe one in the autumn wind‚ôę

07:26.130 --> 07:27.480
and time is limited.

07:27.220 --> 07:30.830
‚ôęHow many times have I seen you in my dreams?‚ôę

07:29.720 --> 07:31.400
I wanted to cultivate Eternity

07:31.430 --> 07:32.780
to repay his kindness.

07:31.870 --> 07:34.890
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

07:33.930 --> 07:35.380
But along the way,

07:35.420 --> 07:37.170
I realise that the process of cultivating Eternity

07:35.650 --> 07:38.860
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

07:37.200 --> 07:38.640
is also a journey of spiritual cultivation,

07:39.360 --> 07:40.720
an inner cultivation.

07:39.480 --> 07:42.990
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

07:41.830 --> 07:42.830
Gaining,

07:42.860 --> 07:43.760
losing,

07:43.620 --> 07:46.110
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

07:44.420 --> 07:45.360
pain,

07:45.590 --> 07:46.640
laughter,

07:46.960 --> 07:50.390
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

07:47.290 --> 07:48.440
for myself

07:48.460 --> 07:49.870
and for many people.

07:50.760 --> 07:52.270
Mortals live a hundred years,

07:50.830 --> 07:54.010
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

07:52.290 --> 07:53.670
Eternals and demons live a thousand.

07:53.960 --> 07:55.440
and deities live on forever.

07:54.820 --> 07:57.950
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

07:56.140 --> 07:57.700
It's already so hard to be a human.

07:58.260 --> 07:59.700
How much harder it is

07:59.100 --> 08:01.830
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

08:00.250 --> 08:01.690
to be an Eternal or even a deity?

08:02.180 --> 08:03.270
I understand.

08:02.550 --> 08:05.410
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

08:04.030 --> 08:05.190
So in Ning'an City,

08:05.190 --> 08:06.310
I chose to hide it from you

08:06.330 --> 08:08.500
because I didn't want you to get entangled in this mess.

08:09.320 --> 08:11.350
Now I choose to tell you everything

08:11.370 --> 08:12.860
because I've figured it out.

08:12.880 --> 08:14.670
No matter what happens in the future,

08:15.940 --> 08:17.570
I will walk the path with you.

08:19.430 --> 08:21.040
But your journey

08:21.220 --> 08:23.260
shouldn't have been troubled in the first place.

08:23.400 --> 08:24.190
Chong Zhao.

08:24.910 --> 08:26.990
You were meant to be a sword-wielding,

08:27.160 --> 08:29.210
justice-defending Lanling Eternal.

08:29.230 --> 08:30.300
Don't ruin you life

08:30.330 --> 08:31.440
because of me.

08:31.660 --> 08:33.659
You sneaking into the Cold Spring Palace was an act of righteousness.

08:33.720 --> 08:34.909
But I hope

08:34.929 --> 08:36.590
you can also protect yourself.

08:36.610 --> 08:38.330
If you know the road ahead is a dead end,

08:38.360 --> 08:39.549
you should turn around quickly.

08:39.570 --> 08:40.909
Don't sacrifice for nothing,

08:40.940 --> 08:42.230
especially for me.

08:43.850 --> 08:45.170
But your safety

08:45.910 --> 08:47.440
is my wish.

08:48.440 --> 08:49.920
But I can't bear your wish.

08:49.940 --> 08:51.350
But it's fine when it comes to Fan Yue?

08:52.960 --> 08:55.230
Just because both of you have to collect Contemplation,

08:56.300 --> 08:57.850
you can walk the same path?

08:59.340 --> 09:00.530
It's because I like him.

09:00.560 --> 09:01.940
It's because I like him.

09:12.960 --> 09:16.350
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

09:16.570 --> 09:19.710
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

09:19.470 --> 09:21.260
Even if we go our separate ways

09:20.360 --> 09:23.690
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

09:21.280 --> 09:22.610
and have our own difficulties,

09:22.880 --> 09:24.120
I still like him.

09:24.890 --> 09:27.560
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

09:26.330 --> 09:27.290
After all,

09:28.120 --> 09:31.740
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

09:31.070 --> 09:32.840
it's because the person you like

09:32.170 --> 09:35.420
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

09:35.020 --> 09:36.370
is not me.

09:35.860 --> 09:39.110
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

09:40.230 --> 09:42.800
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

09:43.940 --> 09:47.330
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

09:44.650 --> 09:47.060
You wanted to tell me these long ago, didn't you?

09:48.370 --> 09:49.810
In the past,

09:50.320 --> 09:51.750
we were childhood friends.

09:53.610 --> 09:55.370
When I was in Ning'an City,

09:55.400 --> 09:57.400
I didn't even know what love is.

09:57.770 --> 10:00.130
But after the experience with the Fox Clan,

10:00.790 --> 10:01.740
being parted by life

10:01.760 --> 10:03.120
and death,

10:02.010 --> 10:05.530
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

10:03.210 --> 10:04.750
and guarding for a thousang years,

10:05.480 --> 10:07.410
my heart died to the passage of time.

10:05.820 --> 10:09.030
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

10:08.720 --> 10:09.570
Chong Zhao.

10:09.620 --> 10:12.980
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

10:10.410 --> 10:12.370
Love is the most precious thing

10:12.400 --> 10:13.960
in the world.

10:13.880 --> 10:16.640
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

10:14.690 --> 10:16.500
It deserves to be treated fairly.

10:17.520 --> 10:20.880
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

10:17.720 --> 10:19.690
I didn't choose you in the Outlanders' City.

10:20.010 --> 10:21.790
Even if I have every reason to,

10:21.200 --> 10:24.470
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

10:22.520 --> 10:24.520
my heart has given me the answer.

10:25.040 --> 10:27.240
You should move on to your own life path.

10:25.270 --> 10:28.450
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

10:29.500 --> 10:32.080
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

10:48.540 --> 10:49.420
What are you here for?

10:50.680 --> 10:52.110
I want to talk to you, Master

10:52.700 --> 10:53.910
about the Weak Water Stone.

10:54.740 --> 10:56.430
Auntie told me everything.

10:57.690 --> 10:59.420
I want to make a deal with you.

10:59.830 --> 11:01.250
I'll give you the Weak Water Stone,

11:01.670 --> 11:02.790
and you'll go and save Ms. Bai.

11:03.570 --> 11:04.810
But I ask Master

11:05.490 --> 11:07.200
to protect Auntie for me.

11:07.840 --> 11:09.600
You will die if the Weak Water Stone leaves your body.

11:10.630 --> 11:11.600
I know.

11:12.720 --> 11:13.720
So,

11:14.160 --> 11:16.070
I hope you don't tell Tian Huo about this.

11:17.480 --> 11:18.290
I can't.

11:18.780 --> 11:19.780
I don‚Äôt agree.

11:20.800 --> 11:21.990
I don't want to take advantage of others.

11:22.430 --> 11:24.190
If Bai Shuo were here, she also wouldn‚Äôt.

11:24.630 --> 11:25.560
And there's Tian Huo.

11:25.940 --> 11:27.750
She finally have feelings for someone after all these years.

11:28.240 --> 11:29.450
What would happen to her when you die?

11:29.470 --> 11:30.660
But for you, Master,

11:31.330 --> 11:32.420
there is no other choice.

11:32.450 --> 11:33.320
If Ms. Bai died,

11:33.320 --> 11:34.200
what would happen to you?

11:34.470 --> 11:35.710
I will think of other ways.

11:35.740 --> 11:37.020
If there were so many ways,

11:37.420 --> 11:38.440
you wouldn't have

11:38.440 --> 11:40.030
spent so much time in Jingyou Mountain.

11:41.100 --> 11:42.350
My life, Mu Jiu's,

11:42.470 --> 11:43.600
was saved by Ms. Bai and Master

11:43.600 --> 11:45.120
from the realm of resentment.

11:45.500 --> 11:46.740
Returning it now

11:47.780 --> 11:49.390
is considered a worthwhile death.

11:49.840 --> 11:52.320
Bai Shuo and I only gave you a start.

11:53.260 --> 11:54.940
Your life was given by your aunt.

11:54.960 --> 11:55.920
Precisely.

11:56.560 --> 11:58.760
All the more reason I can't let Auntie die because of me.

12:00.440 --> 12:01.750
Rong Xian killed people from the Fox Clan,

12:02.900 --> 12:04.470
hence the Fox Clan resented Linglong.

12:05.580 --> 12:07.380
Linglong has been cursed for years,

12:08.990 --> 12:10.680
so Auntie resented the Fox Clan

12:10.700 --> 12:12.380
and sent Qi to death,

12:12.810 --> 12:14.400
at the same time sacrificed her own life.

12:15.580 --> 12:16.340
Guilt,

12:16.370 --> 12:16.890
hatred,

12:16.910 --> 12:17.660
and resent.

12:17.690 --> 12:19.420
These are things that are endless.

12:19.450 --> 12:20.410
One loop after another,

12:20.430 --> 12:21.360
one step chasing the next,

12:21.390 --> 12:22.600
it goes on forever without an end.

12:24.120 --> 12:25.960
If someone has to end it,

12:26.410 --> 12:28.330
the most suitable person is me.

12:28.880 --> 12:29.710
So,

12:31.630 --> 12:33.560
you do this to fulfill everyone's wish

12:34.570 --> 12:36.140
and end all tragedies?

12:36.740 --> 12:37.870
Master,

12:38.740 --> 12:39.900
you word it too altrusticly.

12:41.140 --> 12:42.160
Me?

12:42.360 --> 12:43.500
I am just a little fox

12:44.670 --> 12:46.510
who was lucky to earn a chance to live.

12:47.360 --> 12:49.210
I was born with a shocking background,

12:49.630 --> 12:51.750
have been receiving the deepest and most profound protection,

12:53.150 --> 12:54.600
and even became

12:54.620 --> 12:55.880
the Master of a mountain,

12:55.900 --> 12:57.180
and had a moment of glory.

12:57.400 --> 12:58.630
The luckiest thing

13:00.520 --> 13:02.640
was to have met a girl whom I love,

13:03.170 --> 13:04.660
and she happens to like me too.

13:04.940 --> 13:06.980
Ordinary people might be fortunate to have one or two,

13:07.010 --> 13:08.370
but I, Mu Jiu, have achieved them all.

13:08.810 --> 13:09.570
It's worthwhile!

13:20.210 --> 13:20.930
Fan Yue.

13:22.030 --> 13:23.490
Can I call you that?

13:30.780 --> 13:31.860
In my body,

13:33.400 --> 13:35.720
there is the power you left in me that had changed my fate.

13:37.550 --> 13:38.840
It has been kept for a thousand years.

13:39.570 --> 13:41.470
It was then nourished by the Weak Water Stone,

13:42.140 --> 13:44.540
enough to extend the lifespan of the Emotion Tree by thousands of years.

13:44.880 --> 13:46.560
When the Weak Water Stone is handed over to Ms. Bai,

13:47.100 --> 13:48.500
I request you

13:49.310 --> 13:51.370
to bury the remaining power under the Emotion Tree.

13:51.900 --> 13:52.860
However,

13:53.140 --> 13:54.660
extracting its power

13:55.320 --> 13:56.850
is another life-risking act.

13:57.130 --> 13:58.370
It's very dangerous.

13:59.530 --> 14:00.700
Are you willing to help me?

14:03.300 --> 14:04.520
There's a saying among the Human Race,

14:05.950 --> 14:07.360
"unfamiliar at first, but more familiar after a second encounter."

14:07.990 --> 14:08.800
Master...

14:11.540 --> 14:12.230
I...

14:15.310 --> 14:16.580
Will do my best.

14:17.770 --> 14:19.270
You don‚Äôt address yourself as Master anymore?

14:19.550 --> 14:20.620
Are you

14:21.090 --> 14:22.090
acknowledging me?

14:23.740 --> 14:25.010
About Tian Huo...

14:29.740 --> 14:31.420
I'll say goodbye to her properly.

14:32.500 --> 14:33.860
She deserves better.

14:45.240 --> 14:46.360
Don't touch it.

14:46.390 --> 14:47.270
Behave yourself.

14:49.460 --> 14:50.960
This is the evil insect

14:50.960 --> 14:52.320
caused the bloodshed among the Human Race?

14:52.350 --> 14:53.140
Yes.

14:53.160 --> 14:56.020
I personally intercepted this in Ning'an City.

14:56.080 --> 14:58.280
Otherwise, the new governor Bai Yu

14:58.300 --> 14:59.370
would have died.

14:59.950 --> 15:03.090
It seems that the letter of Chong Zhao is right.

15:03.300 --> 15:04.570
The Cold Spring Palace

