‚ôęOn the vast sea, you and I‚ôę

34:50.350 --> 34:52.210
‚ôęMay I ask, what do the gods see in the world?‚ôę

34:52.449 --> 34:54.550
‚ôęSadness from infatuation, anger, and parting‚ôę

34:54.610 --> 34:56.400
‚ôęMy love brought tears‚ôę

34:56.650 --> 34:58.490
‚ôęGreed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness‚ôę

34:58.790 --> 35:00.620
‚ôęI was never a flower, but I withered on my own‚ôę

35:00.830 --> 35:02.070
‚ôęI fell between your brows and became a good fruit‚ôę

35:02.460 --> 35:03.860
‚ôęThe grand dream of life is hard to let go‚ôę

35:04.450 --> 35:06.240
‚ôęSearching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing‚ôę

35:06.790 --> 35:08.370
‚ôęWith a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions‚ôę

35:08.620 --> 35:10.230
‚ôęI cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon‚ôę

35:10.540 --> 35:12.650
‚ôęThe daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright‚ôę

35:12.960 --> 35:14.540
‚ôęThrough the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky‚ôę

35:14.860 --> 35:16.650
‚ôęI am but a mortal, destined to fade‚ôę

35:16.920 --> 35:18.930
‚ôęBut I went through a thousand calamities for a promise‚ôę

35:19.220 --> 35:20.720
‚ôęI severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me‚ôę

35:20.920 --> 35:23.380
‚ôęTo protect the world for eternity‚ôę

36:44.120 --> 36:45.120
Fan Yue!

36:45.660 --> 36:46.590
This is...

36:47.030 --> 36:48.490
This is Mu Jiu's love.

36:50.640 --> 36:51.690
What about Mu Jiu?

36:53.200 --> 36:54.070
He's dead.

36:56.450 --> 36:58.370
We still can't save him, can we?

36:59.570 --> 37:01.550
This is his choice, Bai Shuo.

37:02.480 --> 37:03.620
My father's death

37:03.900 --> 37:05.420
was his own choice.

37:06.500 --> 37:07.630
Qi's death

37:08.260 --> 37:09.970
was his own choice.

37:11.070 --> 37:12.070
Why are there always

37:12.070 --> 37:13.890
so many cruel choices in this world?

37:13.970 --> 37:16.110
Why is there no perfect solution?

37:16.280 --> 37:18.470
Why can't we live well

37:18.790 --> 37:20.340
with our loved ones?

37:22.050 --> 37:23.540
Deities generate all things,

37:23.610 --> 37:25.080
enduring the hardship of cultivation.

37:25.220 --> 37:26.970
These endless decisions

37:27.330 --> 37:28.810
could be a way of cultivation.

37:29.230 --> 37:30.380
If so,

37:31.740 --> 37:33.670
what's the point of getting stronger?

37:34.850 --> 37:36.280
There are Eternals and demons beyond humans,

37:36.590 --> 37:38.110
deities beyond Eternals and demons.

37:38.880 --> 37:40.520
Even if you become a deity,

37:41.630 --> 37:44.040
can you escape these feelings of helplessness

37:44.380 --> 37:45.630
and return to freedom?

37:48.170 --> 37:49.150
I don't know.

37:50.080 --> 37:51.140
But I know

37:52.050 --> 37:53.920
death does not necessarily lead to an end.

37:54.580 --> 37:56.300
Mu Jiu was calm when he left.

38:03.330 --> 38:04.880
He even asked me to give this to you.

38:11.700 --> 38:12.540
Ms. Bai,

38:12.780 --> 38:14.370
when you see this,

38:14.400 --> 38:16.000
I probably have died.

38:16.020 --> 38:16.750
So,

38:16.780 --> 38:18.090
you have to take this chance

38:18.110 --> 38:20.420
to remember my handsome face.

38:21.450 --> 38:23.450
Recently, I've been thinking...

38:23.480 --> 38:24.320
Demons

38:24.390 --> 38:25.830
are actually just like humans.

38:25.860 --> 38:27.160
We are foolish too.

38:26.890 --> 38:33.750
‚ôęIf the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers‚ôę

38:27.400 --> 38:28.840
For the past twenty years,

38:28.860 --> 38:30.150
I never thought

38:30.180 --> 38:32.000
I would sacrifice my life for others

38:32.520 --> 38:33.920
like a hero.

38:34.240 --> 38:40.120
‚ôęThe moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place‚ôę

38:34.670 --> 38:35.930
The old Mu Jiu

38:35.960 --> 38:36.900
was childish

38:36.930 --> 38:37.860
and willful.

38:37.880 --> 38:38.550
Things like

38:38.580 --> 38:39.390
responsibilities

38:39.410 --> 38:40.000
and morality

38:40.030 --> 38:41.440
are bullshit to me.

38:41.540 --> 38:43.460
But when did it change?

38:41.670 --> 38:44.410
‚ôęAs the wind stirs, the clouds gather‚ôę

38:44.490 --> 38:45.740
Probably

38:45.390 --> 38:48.760
‚ôęAs the clouds shift, the moon becomes full‚ôę

38:46.500 --> 38:47.720
at the Outlanders' City

38:48.180 --> 38:50.130
when I got to know you two.

38:49.140 --> 38:55.530
‚ôęLove is the hardest thing to understand‚ôę

38:51.770 --> 38:53.260
I started to have friends

38:53.310 --> 38:54.430
and family.

38:56.120 --> 38:57.570
Besides Auntie,

38:56.390 --> 39:03.240
‚ôęI'm finally back to where it all started‚ôę

38:58.870 --> 38:59.710
Ah Huo was the first person

38:59.710 --> 39:01.160
who saved me when I was in danger.

39:02.300 --> 39:03.850
Ms. Bai, you're the second one.

39:03.750 --> 39:10.240
‚ôęAll the answers are already explained‚ôę

39:06.760 --> 39:08.510
I really like Ah Huo.

39:08.530 --> 39:09.480
So,

39:09.950 --> 39:12.410
can you take good care of her for me?

39:11.440 --> 39:13.920
‚ôęI'll owe you all of my life‚ôę

39:14.630 --> 39:17.770
‚ôęBut we're destined to part‚ôę

39:18.390 --> 39:24.740
‚ôęHow can I downplay this?‚ôę

39:20.340 --> 39:20.900
Right!

39:21.480 --> 39:22.670
There's also Master.

39:22.740 --> 39:24.280
Before I met you,

39:24.310 --> 39:25.980
I thought you were someone

39:25.340 --> 39:28.570
‚ôęWhen you engrave your love into my heart‚ôę

39:26.290 --> 39:28.130
who could kill people without blinking.

39:28.520 --> 39:29.850
But now I realize

39:28.960 --> 39:32.130
‚ôęWhen my star falls only for you‚ôę

39:29.870 --> 39:31.460
you are just an ordinary demon

39:31.710 --> 39:33.720
who would get worried for your friends

39:32.890 --> 39:34.270
‚ôęWhen the heavens fall‚ôę

39:34.450 --> 39:36.450
and fall in love with people.

39:34.760 --> 39:39.850
‚ôęI can still connect with you through the waning moon‚ôę

39:38.290 --> 39:39.990
Now I finally understand,

39:40.240 --> 39:43.050
‚ôęWhen my pain blurs my eyes‚ôę

39:40.710 --> 39:42.020
whether it's human

39:42.050 --> 39:43.220
or demons,

39:43.660 --> 39:47.670
‚ôęOut of the countless stars, I see only you‚ôę

39:43.920 --> 39:45.460
as long as you have attachments,

39:45.700 --> 39:48.180
you'll have a reason to  willingly stay.

39:48.250 --> 39:57.240
‚ôęAs you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart‚ôę

39:49.820 --> 39:50.920
Ms. Bai,

39:51.120 --> 39:52.560
I gave you the Weak Water Stone willingly.

39:52.580 --> 39:53.500
I don't blame anyone.

39:54.040 --> 39:55.560
My life, Mu Jiu's,

39:55.650 --> 39:58.150
has ended all the love and hatred of the Jingyou Mountain.

39:58.670 --> 39:59.710
In the future,

39:59.740 --> 40:00.750
promise me,

40:01.110 --> 40:02.460
on my behalf,

40:03.420 --> 40:04.850
do not fear anyone

40:04.870 --> 40:05.990
or anything.

40:07.370 --> 40:08.820
Continue to fight endlessly

40:09.020 --> 40:10.000
against fate.

40:20.000 --> 40:24.740
‚ôęI'm finally back to where it all started‚ôę

40:27.640 --> 40:32.940
‚ôęAll the answers are already explained‚ôę

40:35.300 --> 40:37.600
‚ôęI'll owe you all of my life‚ôę

40:38.610 --> 40:41.540
‚ôęBut we're destined to part‚ôę

40:42.250 --> 40:47.780
‚ôęHow can I downplay this?‚ôę

40:48.780 --> 40:51.560
‚ôęWhen you engrave your love into my heart‚ôę

40:52.090 --> 40:55.110
‚ôęWhen my star falls only for you‚ôę

40:55.440 --> 40:57.170
‚ôęWhen the heavens fall‚ôę

40:58.030 --> 41:02.770
‚ôęI can still connect with you through the waning moon‚ôę

41:02.630 --> 41:04.410
People say

41:03.220 --> 41:06.000
‚ôęWhen my pain blurs my eyes‚ôę

41:05.460 --> 41:07.320
