41:19.660 --> 41:23.320
‚ôęWhen you engrave your love into my heart‚ôę

41:21.820 --> 41:23.210
I don't blame you anymore

41:23.650 --> 41:26.040
‚ôęWhen my star falls only for you‚ôę

41:26.790 --> 41:28.380
‚ôęWhen the heavens fall‚ôę

41:26.860 --> 41:29.310
I will remember what you said.

41:29.200 --> 41:33.650
‚ôęI can still connect with you through the waning moon‚ôę

41:30.230 --> 41:31.350
Tian Huo

41:33.790 --> 41:36.050
will be live freely forever.

41:34.580 --> 41:36.890
‚ôęWhen my pain blurs my eyes‚ôę

41:38.290 --> 41:41.820
‚ôęOut of the countless stars, I see only you‚ôę

41:42.950 --> 41:53.070
‚ôęAs you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart‚ôę

42:16.340 --> 42:17.110
You

42:17.140 --> 42:19.440
