42:19.580 --> 42:20.830
Do you trust me now?

42:21.240 --> 42:22.910
Nothing about trust.

42:26.470 --> 42:28.490
We are just demons from the Cold Spring Palace.

42:29.010 --> 42:31.040
That's why you saved me.

42:31.470 --> 42:32.810
If anything happens to you,

42:33.880 --> 42:35.730
Master won‚Äôt let me go.

42:36.030 --> 42:38.540
The Cold Spring Palace loses Lady Fu Ling,

42:38.880 --> 42:41.030
Lord Chong Zhao can take the place.

42:42.960 --> 42:44.440
Isn‚Äôt that better?

42:45.370 --> 42:48.090
Consider it a way to repay you for saving my life in the Outlanders' City.

42:48.280 --> 42:50.160
I don't want to owe anyone anything.

42:53.100 --> 42:55.260
